    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Clinical diagnosis in which labs may be suggestive but not required\n[1]\nCareful investigation of new medications\nList\nof serum sickness medications\nMild\nleukopenia\nor\nleukocytosis\nESR elevation\nMild\nproteinuria\nMild\nhematuria\nMild serum creatinine elevation\nDecreased C3, C4\nOther labs to obtain:\nCH50\nLFTs\nUrine electrolytes (Na, K, Cr, eosinophils)\nESR and CRP\nViral hepatitis\npanel, HIV, RPR/VDRL",
